description: Try our easy to follow Oven-baked Thai Fishcakes recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Fish cake,Pescatarian,Fish,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Peanut free
name: Ovenbaked Thai Fishcakes Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place the fish, fish sauce, curry paste and sugar in a food processor and whizz until smooth. Stir through the green beans and coriander, then season.

Brush a 12hole muffin tray with the oil, then spoon 2-3 tablespoons of the mixture inside each hole. Lightly press down. Place in a preheated oven, 200°C for 12-15 minutes until golden and cooked through. Serve with sweet chilli sauce and cucumber wedges.
